import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Button,
  VStack,
  Heading,
  Text,
  Container,
  Icon,
  Flex,
  Badge,
} from '@chakra-ui/react';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import { useAuth } from '../contexts/AuthContext';
import { FiShield, FiLock } from 'react-icons/fi';

const Login = () => {
  const { login } = useAuth();
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  const handleLogin = () => {
    login();
    navigate('/');
  };

  return (
    <Box
      minH="100vh"
      bgGradient="linear-gradient(135deg, #13151F 0%, #1E2137 100%)"
      position="relative"
      overflow="hidden"
    >
      {/* Animated gradient orbs */}
      <Box
        position="absolute"
        top="-20%"
        right="-10%"
        width="600px"
        height="600px"
        background="radial-gradient(circle, rgba(149, 128, 255, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%)"
        filter="blur(60px)"
        animation="pulse 8s infinite"
      />
      <Box
        position="absolute"
        bottom="-30%"
        left="-15%"
        width="800px"
        height="800px"
        background="radial-gradient(circle, rgba(128, 255, 234, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%)"
        filter="blur(60px)"
        animation="pulse 10s infinite"
      />
      
      <Container maxW="container.md" py={20} position="relative">
        <VStack spacing={8}>
          <Badge
            colorScheme="purple"
            py={2}
            px={6}
            borderRadius="full"
            textTransform="uppercase"
            letterSpacing="wider"
            fontSize="sm"
            bgGradient="linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(149, 128, 255, 0.2), rgba(128, 255, 234, 0.2))"
            border="1px solid"
            borderColor="whiteAlpha.200"
            backdropFilter="blur(10px)"
          >
            Enterprise Security Platform
          </Badge>
          
          <Box
            p={12}
            borderRadius="3xl"
            bg="rgba(26, 28, 42, 0.5)"
            borderWidth="1px"
            borderColor="rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)"
            boxShadow="0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37)"
            backdropFilter="blur(20px)"
            w="full"
            position="relative"
            overflow="hidden"
          >
            {/* Glowing border effect */}
            <Box
              position="absolute"
              top="-50%"
              left="-50%"
              width="200%"
              height="200%"
              background="conic-gradient(from 90deg at 50% 50%, #9580FF 0deg, #80FFEA 90deg, transparent 180deg, transparent 360deg)"
              opacity="0.1"
              animation="rotate 8s linear infinite"
            />
            <VStack spacing={10} position="relative" zIndex={1}>
              <Box
                p={4}
                borderRadius="2xl"
                bgGradient="linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(149, 128, 255, 0.2), rgba(128, 255, 234, 0.2))"
                borderWidth="1px"
                borderColor="whiteAlpha.200"
              >
                <Icon as={FiShield} w={16} h={16} color="#9580FF" />
              </Box>
              
              <VStack spacing={6}>
                <VStack spacing={3}>
                  <Heading 
                    size="2xl" 
                    bgGradient="linear-gradient(135deg, #9580FF, #80FFEA)"
                    bgClip="text"
                    textAlign="center"
                    letterSpacing="tight"
                    lineHeight="shorter"
                  >
                    Welcome to ThreatIntel AI
                  </Heading>
                  <Text 
                    color="whiteAlpha.900" 
                    textAlign="center" 
                    fontSize="xl"
                    maxW="md"
                    letterSpacing="wide"
                  >
                    Your comprehensive cybersecurity threat intelligence platform
                  </Text>
                </VStack>

                <VStack spacing={4} w="full">
                  <Button
                    size="lg"
                    width="full"
                    height="68px"
                    bgGradient="linear-gradient(135deg, #9580FF, #80FFEA)"
                    color="white"
                    fontSize="lg"
                    fontWeight="medium"
                    _hover={{
                      bgGradient: "linear-gradient(135deg, #8070EF, #70EFDA)",
                      transform: "translateY(-2px)",
                      boxShadow: "0 8px 32px rgba(149, 128, 255, 0.4)",
                    }}
                    _active={{
                      transform: "translateY(1px)",
                    }}
                    leftIcon={<Icon as={FiLock} w={5} h={5} />}
                    onClick={handleLogin}
                    position="relative"
                    overflow="hidden"
                    _before={{
                      content: '""',
                      position: "absolute",
                      top: 0,
                      left: 0,
                      width: "100%",
                      height: "100%",
                      bgGradient: "linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), rgba(255,255,255,0))",
                      transform: "translateX(-100%)",
                      transition: "transform 0.6s ease-in-out",
                    }}
                    _hover={{
                      _before: {
                        transform: "translateX(100%)",
                      }
                    }}
                  >
                    Enter Secure Dashboard
                  </Button>
                  
                  <Text 
                    color="whiteAlpha.700" 
                    fontSize="sm"
                    display="flex"
                    alignItems="center"
                    gap={2}
                  >
                    <Icon as={FiShield} />
                    Protected by advanced AI-powered security
                  </Text>
                </VStack>
              </VStack>
            </VStack>
          </Box>
        </VStack>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Login;
